text: Input/Output Data The Input/Output data is the type of data an agent expects and delivers. The SAP Batch agent collects and emits UDRs of the 'sapcc' and 'sapcc.batch' type. For further information, see SAP CC Batch UDRs . MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM p aramete rs, see Administration and Management in Legacy Desktop . Publishes The SAP CC Batch agent does not publish any MIM resources. Accesses The SAP CC Batch agent does not access any MIM resources.
